pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'times new roman\'\">年，&ldquo;数据结构&rdquo;课程被评为江西省精品课程；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_gb2312\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 26pt; text-indent: -67.15pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 67.15pt; mso-char-indent-count: -4.46; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_gb2312\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2007</font></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_gb2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'times new roman\'\">年，教改项目&ldquo;计算机类本科生自主学习设计的多方位整合与多途径实现&rdquo;获江西省教学成果一等奖；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_gb2312\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 26pt; text-indent: -67.15pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 67.15pt; mso-char-indent-count: -4.46; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_gb2312\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2007</font></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_gb2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'times new roman\'\">年，</span></b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"楷体_gb2312\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><b>&ldquo;网络技术基础实验中心&rdquo;被评为江西高校实验教学示范中心 ；</b></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 26pt; text-indent: -67.15pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 67.15pt; mso-char-indent-count: -4.46; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"mso-bookmark: ole_link2\"><span style=\"mso-bookmark: ole_link3\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_gb2312\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2007</font></span></b></span></span><span style=\"mso-bookmark: ole_link2\"><span style=\"mso-bookmark: ole_link3\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_gb2312; color: black; font-s