size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: \'verdana\', \'sans-serif\'; color: #323616; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #323616; mso-ascii-font-family: verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">．若重修课程与现修课程冲突，可凭听课（准考）证到重修课任课老师处办理免听手续；若重修课程与现修课程考试时间冲突，在考前一周办理相关的缓考手续，原则上先保证重修课程的考试，现修课程办理缓考。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'verdana\', \'sans-serif\'; color: #323616; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: \'verdana\', \'sans-serif\'; color: #323616; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #323616; mso-ascii-font-family: verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">．请各学院务必做好学生的重修选课指导工作，若在报名选课时遇到问题，可及时与教务员老师联系，或在教务处留言板上留言，以保证所有学生都能在规定时内报名选课重修。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'verdana\', \'sans-serif\'; color: #323616; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: \'verdana\', \'sans-serif\'; color: #323616; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #323616; mso-ascii-font-family: verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">．重修选课结束后，教务处将选课数据下发至各院、系，请及时通知各任课老师。考试时务必要清点重修人数并检查证件。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'verdana\', \'sans-serif\'; color: #323616; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: \'verdana\', \'sans-serif\'; color: #323616; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #323616; mso-ascii-font-family: verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">．部分学籍已异动的学生，请在新的编入班级办理重修报名相关手续。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'verdana\', \'sans-serif\'; color: #323616; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: \'verdana\', \'sans-serif\'; color: #323616; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: \'verdana\', \'sans-serif\'; color: #323616; mso-bidi-font-family: arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&n