教授就教学过程管理、试卷、毕业论文等教学资料的规范、整理、归档等工作谈了他们的经验。副院长朱华生教授就</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \'times new roman\'\">实验室建设和</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 14pt\">日常管理</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \'times new roman\'\">、校外实训基地建设工作及审核评估中应注意的问题谈了他的看法。</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 14pt\">调研小组还考察了信息工程学院审核评估支撑材料和日常教学相关资料的档案等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 25.5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.82\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 14pt\"><font color=\"#000000\">通过本次调研，增进了两个学院之间的了解，加强了教学管理经验的共享，使我们对审核评估工作的工作思路更加清晰。对我院迎评工作具有非常好的学习借鉴价值，对积极推进落实我院审核评估工作具有很强的指导作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n    \r\n   \r\n                    </div>\r\n                        <br>\r\n                        \r\n                        <div class=\"page_css\">\r\n                            <span id=\"pe100_page_contentpage\" class=\"pagecss\"></span></div>\r\n                        <div class=\"clear\">\r\n                        </div>\r\n<!--                        <div class=\"article_mood\">\r\n                            <div id=\"moodVote\">\r\n  <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"bottom\"><img src=\"/Images/MoodIcon/motion_01.gif\"></td>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"bottom\"><img src=\"/Images/MoodIcon/motion_02.gif\"></td>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"bottom\"><img src=\"/Images/MoodIcon/motion_03.gif\"></td>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"bottom\"><img src=\"/Images/MoodIcon/motion_04.gif\"></td>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"bottom\"><img src=\