</span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 26pt; text-indent: 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">六、其他注意事项<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 26pt; text-indent: 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">．我考点只接纳本校在校生报名，不接纳社会考生。本校学生严禁跨校报考。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 26pt; text-indent: 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">．考生如在报名过程中发现本人信息有误，请先在网上报名系统里提交修改申请，然后在规定的网报时间内，携带相关证明材料至教务处考试中心<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>明德楼<span lang=\"EN-US\">B118)</span>审核、确认所提交的修改信息。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 26pt; text-indent: 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">．考生遇到<span lang=\"EN-US\">CET</span>网报相关问题时，可在报名系统中“留言板”里进行咨询，考点会及时做出解答。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 26pt; text-indent: 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">．此次考试报名费全部实行网上支付，不提供其他缴费途径。请报名考生登录网上报名系统后仔细阅读左上角<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>缴费须知<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>中的相关内容，并在规定的时间内完成网上缴费，未成功完成网上缴费的考生，其报名无效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 26pt; text-indent: 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">．口语考试形式为机考，具体考试形式及内容参见报名网站上相关视频。受考试承办条件的限制，口语报名人数有上限限制，网上报名系统达到最大报名上限后，将不再接受报名。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 26pt; text-indent: 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">．成绩发布：笔试成绩与口语考试成绩将同时发布。成绩报告单将同时显示笔试和口试成绩，如考生仅参加笔试，成绩报告单照常发放，口试成绩栏部分显示为空。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 20pt; text-indent: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: 5.25pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">．<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月的大学英语四六级成绩已经发布在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://jwc.nchu.edu.cn/\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">http://jwc.nchu.edu.cn/</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">（教务处主页——信息查询——等级考试信息查询）中，考生可以下载查询。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 20pt; text-indent: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">．教务处考试中心联系电话：<span lang=\"EN-US\">83863713</span>李老师，殷老师<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 20pt; text-indent: 217pt; mso-char-indent-count: 15.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>2017</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n    \r\n   \r\n                    </div>\r\n                      