INSERT INTO `page_context` VALUES ('519', '32', '软件学院召开本科教学工作审核评估动员会', '无', '<div class=\"article_content_list\" id=\"fontzoom\">\r\n                    <div id=\"articleContnet\">\r\n                    \r\n      \r\n     <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">软件学院召开本科教学工作审核评估动员会</font></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">3</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">9</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日，软件学院在学院会议室召开了</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2018</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年教育部对我校进行本科教学工作审核评估动员会。会议由学院院长舒坚主持，学院全体教职工参加了会议。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">会上，舒坚院长就本科教学工作审核评估工作做了动员讲话。首先，舒院长对本科教学工作审核评估的重要性和重大意义进行了分析。强调学院全体教职工一方面要对本次本科教学工作审核评估在思想上引起高度重视，另一方面也要以平常心来对待。他在为大家解读了本次本科教学工作审核评估的内涵的同时，还给大家讲解了</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt\">“审核评估”与“水平评估”两者之间的区别，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">告诉大家“审核评估”</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">是用自己的尺子量自己</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt\">审核结论不分等级，形成写实性审核报告。审核评估的核心是质量，是对学校人才培养目标与培养效果的实现状况进行评价。目的是“保障质量”，重点考察学校办学定位和人才培养目标与社会需求的适应度、教师和教学资源对学校人才培养的保障度、教学和质量保障体系运行及学生和用人单位的满意度。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: \'times new roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-us; mso-fareast-language: zh-cn; mso-bidi-language: ar-sa\">舒院长</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 13.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: \'times new roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-us; mso-fareast-language: zh-cn; mso-bidi-language: ar-sa\">指出，审核评估是政府加强高校宏观调控和分类指导的重要手段，是高校推进内涵建设和提升办学声誉的自身需求，事关学校的社会声誉和办学品牌。他</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: \'times new roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-us; mso-fareast-language: zh-cn; mso-bidi-language: ar-sa\">要求学院全体教职工以本次审核评估为契机，树立大局意识，加强学院的教风、学风建设。对学校的本科教学工作审核评估工作要有清晰的认识，要以高度的责任心和执行力迎接本次教学评估；</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 13.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: \'times new roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-us; mso-fareast-language: zh-cn; mso-bidi-language: ar-sa\">要充分认识审核评估的意义，真正做到思想到位、责任到位和工作到位。全院教职工要将思想统一到学校评建工作的总体部署上来，扎扎实实做好审核评估每一项工作，为圆满完成审核评估、推动学校改革发展作出新的更大贡献。</span></font></p>\r\n\r\n    \r\n   \r\n                    </div>\r\n                        <br>\r\n                        \r\n                        <div class=\"page_css\">\r\n                            <span id=\"pe100_page_contentpage\" class=\"pagecss\"></span></div>\r\n                        <div class=\"clear\">\r\n                        </div>\r\n<!--                        <div class=\"article_mood\">\r\n                            <div id=\"moodVote\">\r\n  <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"bottom\"><img src=\"/Images/MoodIcon/motion_01.gif\"></td>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"bottom\"><img src=\"/Images/MoodIcon/motion_02.gif\"></td>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"bottom\"><img src=\"/Images/Moo